SERIES NORMALIZATION (Backend)
================================================================================

Input examples:
  "Spider-Man #1"
  "Preacher (2019) (Digital)"
  "A Man Among Ye v01 (2021) (Digital) (XRA-Empire)"

Removal process:
  1. Remove .cbr|.cbz|.cb7|.cbt|.pdf extensions
  2. Remove volume/issue numbers: v01, vol 1, #1, 001
  3. Remove years: (2019), [2021]
  4. Remove metadata tags: (Digital), (Empire)

Output examples:
  "Spider-Man"
  "Preacher"
  "A Man Among Ye"

Series Priority:
  1. Use comic.series field if available
  2. Use normalized folder name if in folder
  3. Use normalized filename as fallback

